features: This Original Lip Balm helps protect your lips from the harsh and damaging effects of the wind and cold. Lip relief to last throughout the day, leaving your lips feeling naturally soft, smooth and healthy. It nourishes, hydrates and soothes. Say goodbye to dryness, cracks, inflammation and peeling.
GENTLE ON YOUR LIPS - The lip balm has pleasant and light texture that is comforting and is quickly absorbed.
LONG LASTING - Lip relief within seconds to last throughout the day, leaving your lips feeling naturally soft, smooth and healthy
EASY TO USE - This lip balm is easy to apply and spreads evenly on the lips, leaving a light sheen.
This twin-pack of Pretty Original Moisturising Lip Balm contains 2-Pieces, ideal for one on your desk and the other to-go.
